Author: -Macaronis-
Text: Oh, I had this moment too. I went out to by vitamins for me and there in the same aisle I saw a girl, as tall and as skinny as me, also looking for vitamins. Later I found her near the baby food aisle because I wanted to check out shit there too. Then at the protein bars. Then where the gluten free things were (they have little pretzels there that are less than 300 calories a pack). It's like we were looking at the same shit and I looked at her again and I just knew. I knew she is going through the same. Hope she is doing better.

Author: humanskincalories
Text: Complete strangers who you know have the same exact problem as you is an experience I've never had but I imagine it's like that spiderman meme
